---
<Base title="Qnury.e's" className="flex flex-col gap-4">

    <!-- Landing -->
    <div class="h-[80vh] w-full font-serif px-24 mb-36 flex flex-col gap-8 justify-between *:py-16 *:w-full">
        <div class="text-3xl">
            <h1>欢迎光临 Qnury.e's</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="text-2xl text-end *:tracking-wide *:[word-spacing:0.8rem]">
            <p>切断电缆 朝霞晚风 临时收入 临时生活</p>
            <p>切断电缆 数字云烟 免费月光 免费惊险</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Read More Button -->
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-1/2 bottom-2 flex flex-col gap-0.5 items-center opacity-70">
        <span class="font-serif">SCROLL</span>
        <ChevronDownIcon size={16} />
    </div>

    <!-- About -->
    <div class="h-screen w-full font-serif px-24 flex flex-col gap-8 *:w-full">
        <div class="text-6xl">
